AssetAdjustmentCard is a CardView
    show labels
    main column
        AdjustmentDate
            label is "Adjusted_"
        CreatedBy
            label is "CreatedBy_"
    right column
        AdjustmentStatus
            no label
            display as tag
                color of green when (AdjustmentStatus.Released)
                color of yellow when (AdjustmentStatus.NotReleased)
